What should {{{statnet}}} package do?

1. Facilitate installation of all Statnet Project packages from CRAN.
1. Facilitate installation of some (which?) Statnet Project packages from CRAN.
1. Facilitate updating of Statnet Project packages without too much interaction from CRAN.
1. Facilitate installation/updating of Statnet Project packages from http://www.statnet.org .
1. Facilitate loading of some (which?) packages via {{{library(statnet)}}}.
1. Provide a point of citation.

Please feel free to add more entries at the end.

